Tr70646.@label: Fig. 1. Fumiglobus pieridicola and Conidiocarpus caucasicus, in boldface, represent new sequences from this study and are well supported as members of the Capnodiaceae. This maximum likelihood tree was generated with RAxML for concatenated ribosomal large and small subunit sequences. Numbers are bootstrap values from 500 replicates.
